(846, 98, '_form', '<div class="form-group">\n  <label for="usr">First Name</label>\n  [text* fname class:form-control]\n</div>\n\n<div class="form-group">\n  <label for="usr">Middle Name</label>\n  [text* mname class:form-control]\n</div>\n\n<div class="form-group">\n  <label for="usr">Last Name</label>\n  [text* lname class:form-control]\n</div>\n\n<div class="form-group">\n  <label for="usr">Date of Birth</label>\n  [date dob class:form-control]\n</div>\n\n<div class="form-group">\n  <label for="usr">Age</label>\n  [number age class:form-control]\n</div>\n\n<div class="form-group">\n  <label for="usr">Gender</label>\n  [radio gender class:form-control default:1 "male" "female"]\n</div>\n\n<div class="form-group">\n  <label for="usr">Address</label>\n  [text address class:form-control]\n</div>\n\n<div class="form-group">\n  <label for="usr">City</label>\n  [text city class:form-control]\n</div>\n\n<div class="form-group">\n  <label for="usr">Phone(R)</label>\n  [tel phone_R class:form-control]\n</div>\n\n<div class="form-group">\n  <label for="usr">Phone(O)</label>\n  [tel phone_o class:form-control]\n</div>\n\n<div class="form-group">\n  <label for="usr">Mobile 1 * (For SMS Updates)</label>\n  [tel mobile_1 class:form-control]\n</div>\n\n<div class="form-group">\n  <label for="usr">Mobile 2 * (Parent''s Mobile)</label>\n  [tel mobile_2 class:form-control]\n</div>\n\n<div class="form-group">\n  <label for="usr">Mobile 3 (Participant''s Number)</label>\n  [tel mobile_3 class:form-control]\n</div>\n\n\n<div class="form-group">\n  <label for="usr">Email</label>\n  [email* email_1 class:form-control]\n</div>\n\n<div class="form-group">\n  <label for="usr">Email</label>\n  [email* email_2 class:form-control]\n</div>\n\n<div class="form-group">\n  <label for="usr">School / College Name</label>\n  [text school_college class:form-control]\n</div>\n\n<div class="form-group">\n  <label for="usr">Blood Group</label>\n  [text blood_group class:form-control]\n</div>\n\n<p>\n  Note: It is very important for the participants to go through the program details. <br>If the participant is under any medication or has any allergies, <br>\n  please provide such details to us. Any specific characteristics like night walking, phobias etc.<br> should be mentioned in the space below.  \n</p>\n<p>Remarks</p>\n[textarea remark]\n<p>Do you receive our brochure regularly?  [radio brochure class:form-group default:1 "Yes" "No"]</p>\n<p>[acceptance acceptance] I have read and agree to the Terms &amp; Conditions.</p>\n<p>[acceptance declaration] Declaration</p>\n<p>\nI would like to enroll myself / my ward to participate in the nature / adventure camp organized by you. I am aware of the risks inherent in the camp involving adventure sports / activities during the programme as well as travelling organized and conducted by HASMUKH VAJA / HAVA LIFE. and their agents.<br>\n<br>I hereby state that I / my ward is participating in these adventure sports / activities of my own free will and consent, and understand and agree that HASMUKH VAJA / HAVA LIFE. and their agents take all necessary precautions to minimize the risk and avoid any accidents and ensure safe participation in these adventure sports / activities and are not responsible for any mishaps that may occur while participating.\n<br>I have read the above statement and fully understand its contents. I realize and agree that the same serves as an agreement of release and assumption of risk on myself.\n<br>I declare that the terms and conditions mentioned overleaf have been explained &amp; interpreted to me in my vernacular language and agree to abide by them. I realize and agree that the same serves as an agreement of release and assumption of risk on myself.\n</p>\n\n<div class="form-group">\n   <button type="submit" class="btn btn-default btnsub" name="submit">Submit</button>\n</div>'),
